comments.content:
Thanks everyone, awesome suggestions! You didn’t let me down.

@Stephen: Good point, I was thinking that about Comalle as well. No smaller weights either. I’m a newbie type designer, so any modifications I make will be minimal.

@Jos: Yep, I agree. Rayuela Chocolate italic is right up my alley. Yea, I see the lack of contrast in the caps to lowercase.

@Stefan: Yes, I plan on it! Thanks for the reminder and encouragement as well. (I promise I won’t hack up anyones hard work. If I must, I will contact the type designer directly and ask for their help.)

@poms: I’m considering Sauna, although it looks a little too “fat kid eating marshmallow’s” for this identity. ;)

**Omnes** is a great suggestion, I’m digging that a lot! Will seriously consider.

@Sharon: Thanks for the sample! I’m not quite sure a slab serif feels right. Appreciate the suggestion, of course. =)

I’ll keep you updated on which I decide. Thanks again!
